abstract: >-
  RCT Platform is the open SDK for an intent-centric constitutional AI operating
  system. It implements the FDIA equation (F = D^I x A), the JITNA Protocol
  (RFC-001), SignedAI multi-LLM consensus with ED25519 attestation, and the
  HexaCore 7-model registry. Designed for verifiable, auditable AI decisions
  with a built-in human-in-the-loop guarantee: when A = 0, all output is blocked
  by construction. Built by a solo developer from Bangkok, Thailand.